reviewText: Excellent and informative!  I ordered this CD one week after returning from Israel, and thoroughly enjoyed reliving the destinations of my trip through this well-documented and beautifully filmed video.
Purchased one of these from Svitka, tour guide in Israel.  Now purchasing two more.  Have watched at least three times.  So real.  God bless Israel, and places of our Lord Jesus.
We use this for educational purposes in our Sunday School lessons. It has great information, but can get long to watch.
